Class ContainerWComp

  • java.lang.Object
    • smac.upnp.wcomp.Spy
      • smac.upnp.wcomp.ContainerWComp

  • public class ContainerWComp
extends smac.upnp.wcomp.Spy
    Class that connects to a the structural service provided by the container. This class is used to call the upnp methods from a container.
